n-type FET with a field effect mobility of 0.13 cm$^2$ V$^{-1}$ s$^{-1}$ under no illumination. We collected the output and transfer characteristics of the device under two different wavelength (488 nm $\&$ 632 nm), at 5 different powers for each. The device channel was 3 $\mu$m, hence the laser spot avoided the Au electrodes during illumination and all of the collected photo-generated current originated in the MoS$_2$.\\

